headline: Eastern Bank, Customers Bancorp, Citizens Financial Group, Banc of California, and Flagstar Financial Shares Are Falling, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after hotter-than-expected inflation data and rising concerns over credit risk rattled investors.
